title: "The Agent Colony: A Pattern Language for Self-Governing AI Agent Ecosystems"
message: "If you use or reference this work, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Oliver
    given-names: David
version: "1.1.5"
date-released: 2026-04-13
