keywords:
  - agent colony
  - multi-agent systems
  - agent architecture
  - agent mirror
  - pattern language
  - autonomous agents
  - AI governance
abstract: >
  A universal architectural pattern for self-governing ecosystems of autonomous
  AI agents that persist beyond projects, evolve across technology generations,
  and coexist with human organisations through defined boundaries. The work
  includes six principles, the Agent Mirror identity standard, and analysis of
  six gaps in current standards.
